大政府12日宣布回击美国钢铝关税，将对总计298亿加元（1加元约合0.69美元）的美国商品征收25%的反制关税。 加拿大财政部长勒布朗、外交部长乔利与创新、科学和工业部长商鹏飞共同召开记者会宣布这一反制关税方案，以回应当天美国对所有进口钢铁和铝征收25%关税的举措。这一反制关税涉及的美国商品包括钢铁和铝产品、电脑、运动器材等。 美国对加拿大和墨西哥产品加征25%关税的措施于本月4日生效。作为回应，加拿大已对价值300亿加元的美国产品加征25%的关税，涉及家禽、肉类、奶制品、小麦和其他食品。欧盟和加拿大宣布对美国商品实施反制关税-新华每日电讯"},"attached_info":"CkIIzZWw3cGZhvkBEAMaCTExMzkzNjUzMiCGysW+BjAAOIsBQApyCzE0Nzg0NDM5NTA0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"170 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b115135ef0a89cab96f0c92617e389e4_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1741919179.971156","card_id":"Q_14852785081","target":{"id":14852785081,"title":"如何评价绝区零「零号·安比」的代理人秘闻「白银的复苏」？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/14852785081","type":"question","created":1741849793,"answer_count":32,"follower_count":30,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[166361,2003653],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkEIzZWw3cGZhvkBEAMaCTExMzk1MTE5NSDBicq+BjAAOB5AC3ILMTQ4NTI3ODUwODF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"157 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-2400e0ef894d0c588e605104967d1443_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1741919179.971416","card_id":"Q_14853439206","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":14853439206,"title":"董明珠称格力整套技术是我们自己在白纸上画出来的，格力市场总监称线上店考虑升级为董明珠健康家，如何解读？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/14853439206","type":"question","created":1741850175,"answer_count":72,"follower_count":90,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","ava